These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
There 4 different types of food: grapes, nectarine, zucchini, pear
1. the person eating grapes is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating pear is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Food     | grapes     | zucchini    | pear    | nectarine      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, chinchilla, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Pet   | chinchilla     | goldfish | dog  | rat |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, azure, purple, amber
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the german is between the person who likes blue and the person who likes amber##2
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who likes purple##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person who likes azure and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Color          | blue | azure   | amber     | purple     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the fan of soul is the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Beverage         | mirinda | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | cola   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
House: futuristic, wooden, art-deco, gothic-revival
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the japanese is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the wooden house is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| House         | wooden      | gothic-revival | futuristic      | art-deco |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

