.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
House: wooden, palace, futuristic, cottage
 1. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the palace house is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the nigerian is between the fan of electronic and the fan of country##2
 5. the cottage house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the cottage house is the fan of indie##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the fan of punk and the fan of indie##2
10. the futuristic house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | indie    | electronic | punk    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| House           | futuristic   | cottage    | wooden        | palace   |

