.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, manager, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, march, october
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the librarian is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Job           | software-developer | librarian | fisherman   | manager |
| Birthday   | august         | february     | october     | march |

