3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
