3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the italian is on the right of the colombian##1
6. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the indian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| City           | new-york   | edinburgh    | rome | hannover |
| Nationality   | indian    | colombian | italian    | turkish         |

