3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is the modern house##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the art-deco house##1
7. the art-deco house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | satire | adventure | sports   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | jazz   | indie     | blues    |
| House   | tower  | art-deco | modern  | farmhouse |

